{"tid":663530,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"諗著母親節氹下老母 點知俾佢鬧我去死..","createTime":"2018-05-13T11:18:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T11:30:07.000Z","uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"24f10815366e84134c028089a1ec8e34ce029bf0","tid":663530,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:18:32.000Z","msg":"早午兩餐都請咗阿媽飲茶食飯，諗著講句話氹下佢歡喜，於是講咗<br />\n<br />\n&quot;媽你想要乜嘢我都會努力做。除咗叫我拍拖結婚。呢個真係唔好意思，你永遠做唔到奶奶阿嫲了。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n老母依家仲嬲梗唔睬我。今晚餐飯都唔知食乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 A0, 每用俾8000家用。另外平均每禮拜請屋企人飲茶同陪行街，有時佢地都叫我搵多啲FD 唔好咁群腳"},{"pid":"9246972ab615d322a3977080ac6f63cc87609f8f","tid":663530,"uid":35547,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"氹人 咁你後面果句係做乜鳩"},{"pid":"4928e37e41329cdfe2256c06aae356394f750b58","tid":663530,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9246972ab615d322a3977080ac6f63cc87609f8f","tid":663530,"uid":35547,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:19:31.000Z","msg":"氹人 咁你後面果句係做乜鳩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"如實反映姐。我已經盡量以其他嘢去彌補架喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb5c9d8293b9ef517f68be6dcd79fccfdcb3475","tid":663530,"uid":138407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:21:52.000Z","msg":"笑死我"},{"pid":"11f5dc6c1250097386e3e1abf54dab75fd61e034","tid":663530,"uid":34676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T11:23:19.000Z","msg":"戇鳩鳩，係咪覺得自己講出口，好有原則，好認命，好有一種天煞孤星嘅Feel<br />\n一年一次母親節，其他時間唔講，係要搵今日講<br />\n我覺得你呢啲自己搵嚟搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaeaf8e9fd84b2140af8ee15a6ba9524898c1efe","tid":663530,"uid":34676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4928e37e41329cdfe2256c06aae356394f750b58","tid":663530,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9246972ab615d322a